dprim-cheap SIGN x (just (inj₁ (just (inj₂ dy)))) = ≤ᵇ⇒≤ tt
dprim-cheap SIGN x (just (inj₂ dy)) = ≤ᵇ⇒≤ tt
dprim-cheap IADD x dy = ≤ᵇ⇒≤ tt
dprim-cheap IMUL x dy = ≤ᵇ⇒≤ tt
